es of Interest and its an ancient Hindu Shrine perched on top of an outcrop amidst constantly crashing waves, the temple is simply among Bali not to be missed icons. The onshore site is dotted with smaller shrines alongside visitors leisure facilities that compromise restaurants, Shops and cultural park presenting regular dance performances. The temple is located in the Beraban village of the Tabanan regency, an approximate 20 km northwest of Kuta and is included on most tours to Bali western and central regions. Return to hotel post the tour and spend the overnight in Bali., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 5 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast and Dinner, Description: Sunset Dinner Cruise By Bounty Cruise (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Morning Free for leisure to explore. Spend an unforgettable evening cruise on Bounty Dinner Cruise, Bali. Take in a breathtaking view of the sunset over Tanjung Benoa. Enjoy a delicious international buffet dinner with your loved ones. Watch various interactive performances, such as a traditional Balinese dance, comedy number and DJ performance. Return to hotel post the tour and spend the overnight in Bali., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 6 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Half Day Water Sports with Uluwatu Temple Tour Followed by Kecak Dance (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Enjoy the Salty Air! Sandy Hair! Feel the tropical breeze and get closer to Indian Ocean with selected water sport activity. 1 x Jet Ski & Banana Boat Ride and Complimentary 1 x Parasailing Later proceed Uluwatu Temple sits on 70-meter-high cliff protruding above Indonesian Ocean. The main site of Uluwatu Tours is visiting this temple. There are hundreds of monkeys roaming along the path outside temple. A small forest lies at the front and hundreds of monkey’s dwells here. They are believed to guard the temple from bad influence. The Serpentine pathway to the temple is fortified by concrete walls on the cliff sides. When sun goes down, we will witness the Theatrical Fire Dance Show ‘Kecak Fire Dance’. Kecak dance is that the accompanying music is provided by the human voice, the gamelan suara, a choir of a hundred men or more sitting in concentric circle, swaying, standing up, lying prone as the story develops. Amongst the swaying masses the voices of the storytellers can be heard telling the unfolding tale. The music generated from a combination sounds of members cak which were about 50 – 70 people all of them will make music in acapella. Return to hotel post the tour and spend the overnight in Bali., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 7 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. Extension Nights: Travel Validity: 01 Oct – 19 Dec 2024 & 07 Jan – 31 Mar 2025 CATEGORY HOTELS PAKAGE COST: PER PERSON IN USD SINGLE TWIN / DOUBLE TRIPLE CHILD WITH BED CHILD NO BED STANDARD Hotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in Bali USD 40 USD 32 USD 32 USD 25 USD 10 VALUE Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali USD 50 USD 50 USD 50 USD 25 USD 10 PREMIUM Hotel Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar in Bali USD 95 USD 90 USD 90 USD 40 USD 15 Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple Child With Bed Child No Bed Standard Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or Similar in Dubai USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Value Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Premium Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Black Out Dates Surcharge - 20-Dec-2024 to 6-Jan-2025 New Year and Christmas // 26 Jan – 02 Feb 2025 Chinese New year // 28 Mar – 03 Apr 2025 Nyepi Day, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nThe price is 83484.0. Hotels envisaged include: \nHotel\xa0Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or\xa0Similar in Bali\n, \nHotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in\xa0Bali\n, \nHotel\xa0Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali\n. Meals include: Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included. Inclusions: 06 nights stay at the selected hotel option or similar in Kuta. Daily breakfast, except on Day 1 Airport / hotel / airport transfers on (PVT Basis) Meet & Greet assistance at the airport English Speaking Driver during Transfer & Tour Half Day Water Sports with Uluwatu Temple Tour Followed by Kecak Dance (PVT Basis) Full Day Kintamani Hot Spring & Ubud village Tour –With Tegalalang Rice Fields (PVT Basis) Sunset Dinner Cruise By Bounty Cruise (PVT Basis) Royal Taman Ayun & Tanah Lot Tour (PVT Basis) Full Day Ubud Bali Swing with Local Lunch & 120 Mins Spa Treatment (PVT Basis) Complimentary Welcome drink upon arrival at the Hotel & Villa Complimentary Balinese Sarong per person (adult only) as welcome gift on arrival (Adult only) Complimentary 01 bottle of Mineral Water per person on arrival Free Wi-Fi at Hotel/Villa/ Resort area Travel Insurance (Valid for the age group till 60 Yrs.). Exclusions: TCS & GST Indonesia Visa Charges Departure PCR test, if applicable All flights service Meals not mentioned in the itinerary. Any tips for guide & Driver Anything not mentioned in the inclusions. Pre & Post tour services & cost Expenditure of a personal nature (Such as uses of Mini – Bar & Refrigerator, laundry service, telephone call, camera fee, tips & Etc) All drink and beverages Hotel promotional rates not valid during Black out Period / Surcharge Dates / Stop Sales on Hotel Tourism Tax (if applicable) Midnight surcharge Blackout Dates: 15 DEC 2024 - 06 JAN 2025 The rates are valid for minimum 02 adults travelling together at all times.. Product Terms and Conditions: Package Terms and Conditions: The upgrade 