with our selected Water Sports Activity. Pick up for Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (Incl. 1 x Jet Ski – Banana Boat Ride) and Complimentary 1 x Parasailing or Flying Fish. Later proceed Uluwatu Temple sits on 70-meter-high cliff protruding above Indonesian Ocean. The main site of Uluwatu Tours is visiting this temple. There are hundreds of monkeys roaming along the path outside temple. A small forest lies at the front and hundreds of monkey’s dwells here. They are believed to guard the temple from bad influence. The Serpentine pathway to the temple is fortified by concrete walls on the cliff sides. When sun goes down, we will witness the Theatrical Fire Dance Show ‘Kecak Fire Dance’. Kecak dance is that the accompanying music is provided by the human voice, the gamelan suara, a choir of a hundred men or more sitting in concentric circle, swaying, standing up, lying prone as the story develops. Amongst the swaying masses the voices of the storytellers can be heard telling the unfolding tale. The music generated from a combination sounds of members cak which were about 50 – 70 people all of them will make music in acapella. Overnight stay at Villa.', 'Day free for Leisure Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today Day is at leisure to explore Bali or shopping at the local market. Overnight stay at Villa.', 'Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The above itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. EXTENSION NIGHTS KUTA: Travel Validity: 01 Oct – 20 Dec 2024 & 07 Jan – 31 Mar 2025 CATEGORY HOTELS PACKAGE COST: PER PERSON IN USD SINGLE TWIN /DOUBLE TRIPLE CHILDWITH BED CHILD NO BED STANDARD Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or similar NA 32 NA NA NA VALUE Antanya Hotel Kuta (Deluxe Room) /Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar NA 50 NA NA NA EXTENSION NIGHTS VILLA: Travel Validity: 01 Oct – 20 Dec 2024 & 07 Jan – 31 Mar 2025 CATEGORY HOTELS PACKAGE COST: PER PERSON 