formation. Many shacks & restaurants lined up along the beach make sure that your tummy is full & you enjoy the most. Includes: - 1 x Jet Ski, Banana Boat. Complimentary 1 x Parasailing or Flying Fish, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 3 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast and Local Lunch, Description: Full Day ATV Ride & Ayung River Rafting with Lunch (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Experience the Ultimate Adventure with Single ATV or Tandem ATV Bali. Discover the thrills of off-road exploration through Bali’s scenic landscape. Unleash your Inner explorer and create lasting memories with single and tandem ride experience in Bali Inclusion: - Clean Towels, Safety Briefing, Boots, Helmet, Personal Insurance (6 – 65 years), Professional ATV Guide, Locker Enjoy Local Lunch. Later proceed to Ayung River Rafting. Ayung river rafting Bali rapid class can be categories and suitable for beginners. So if you are first Timer and not goo swimmer, Ayung River Rafting adventure is suitable for you. Ayung river has 10 KM route and 2 hours rafting duration. Professional rafting guide is always accompanied with you and give you instructions on thing to do during rafting trip. Inclusion: - Free Coffee & Tea, Snack, Safety equipment, Insurance Coverage, Full use of Lockers, Changing Room, Shower including towel & Soap Return to hotel post the tour and spend the overnight in Bali., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 4 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast and Local Lunch, Description: West Nusa Penida Island Tour with Lunch (SIC Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today proceed to enjoy West Nusa Penida Island Tour. Highlights: - Kelingking Beach, Angel Billabong, Broken Beach, Snorkeling Oceanic Pool, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 5 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. Extension Nights: Travel Validity: 01 Oct – 19 Dec 2024 & 07 Jan – 31 Mar 2025 CATEGORY HOTELS PAKAGE COST: PER PERSON IN USD SINGLE TWIN / DOUBLE TRIPLE CHILD WITH BED CHILD NO BED STANDARD Hotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in Bali USD 40 USD 32 USD 32 USD 25 USD 10 VALUE Antanya Hotel Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali USD 50 USD 50 USD 50 USD 25 USD 10 PREMIUM Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar in Bali USD 95 USD 90 USD 90 USD 40 USD 15 Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Standard Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or Similar in Dubai USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Value Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Premium Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Black Out Dates Surcharge - 20-Dec-2024 to 6-Jan-2025 New Year and Christmas // 26 Jan – 02 Feb 2025 Chinese New year // 28 Mar – 03 Apr 2025 Nyepi Day, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nThe price is 70052.0. Hotels envisaged include: \nHotel\xa0Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali\n, \nHotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in\xa0Bali\n, \nHotel\xa0Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or\xa0Similar in Bali\n. Meals include: Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included. Inclusions: 04 nights stay at the selected hotel option or similar in Kuta. Daily breakfast, except on Day 1 Airport / hotel / airport transfers on (PVT Basis) Meet & Greet assistance at the airport English Speaking Driver during Transfer & Tour Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (PVT Basis) Full Day: ATV Ride & Ayung River Rafting with Local Lunch (PVT Basis) West Nusa Penida Island Tour with Local Lunch (SIC Basis) Complimentary Welcome drink upon arrival at the Hotel & Villa Complimentary Balinese Sarong per person (adult only) as welcome gift on arrival (Adult only) Complimentary 01 bottle of Mineral Water per person on arrival Free Wi-Fi at Hotel/Villa/ Resort area Travel Insurance (Valid for the age group till 60 Yrs.). Exclusions: TCS & GST Indonesia Visa Charges Departure PCR test, if applicable All flights service Meals not mentioned in the itinerary. Any tips for guide & Driver Anything not mentioned in the inclusions. Pre & Post tour services & cost Expenditure of a personal nature (Such as uses of Mini – Bar & Refrigerator, laundry service, telephone call, camera fee, tips & Etc) All drink and beverages Hotel promotional rates not valid during Black out Period / Surcharge Dates / Stop Sales on Hotel Tourism Tax (if applicable) Midnight surcharge Blackout Dates: 15 DEC 2024 - 06 JAN 2025 The rates are valid for minimum 02 adults travelling together at all times.. Product Terms and Conditions: Package Terms and Conditions: The upgrade hotel prices are subject to availability at the time of booking. The upgrade hotel prices DO NOT GUARANTEE rooms at the envisaged hotels. The upgrade hotel rooms are subject to availability at the time of booking. For the upgrade hotel, In case the hotel chosen is unavailable we will provide with multiple options of similar category hotel. The rates are valid for minimum 02 adults travelling together at all times. During Peak Season: Minimum 2 Nights Stay is required No Check Out period on 31 December 2024 and 01 January 2025 Nyepi Day (Silent Day) is on 29 March 2025. No outdoor activity is allowed, and Airport will be closed from 05.59 am 29 March 2025 to 06.00 am 30 March 2025 Compulsory New Year Dinner will be Applicable according to the Resort The rates are not valid on block out dates. Surcharges as and when applicable will be advised and passengers would be requested to pay the same Surcharges could be over and above the total package price quoted to the passengers at the time of booking. Guests are requested to check with sales staff before booking their on-wards/connecting flights. The rates are subject to availability of hotel accommodation and sightseeing tours at the time of booking. We reserve the right to use an alternate hotel accommodation of an equal or higher standard. If we source a more expensive alternative, we reserve the right to re-quote based on the higher rates. Prices are not valid during Trade Fair periods. Rates are valid for Indian Passport holders only. International Check in time is 1400 hours / Check out time is 1100 hours, early check in and checkout is subject to availability and cannot be guaranteed. Transfers wherever included are without night surcharges. No refunds either in part or in full will be made for any unutilized service. All the sightseeing tours and excursions are organized by local companies. The timings and days of operation are subject to alteration. Changes if any will be intimated at the time of booking. Sightseeing’s tours are strictly based on whether conditions and also local service providers have rights to cancel the sightseeing tours without prior notice. Rates subject to change without prior notice and also for clients traveling during weekends. Offer if any can be withdrawn at any point without prior notice. Bookings once confirmed are subject to cancellation charges which shall be advised at that time. TCIL is not responsible for any change in the price due to factors not in the control of the organization. As a practice all international hotels charge a security deposit via credit card or cash, at the time of check- in for each room. The amount will vary according to the hotel and is refunded back to the clients upon check-out. Debit cards should not be offered as it will be charged immediately and refunded only after 2-3 weeks. If any additional services or mini bar or any other service is utilized at the hotel, the hotel reserves the right to charge the same on this security deposit provided by the client. TCIL would not be responsible for these transactions and these are solely between the hotels and the clients.. Highlights of the package: .", 'packageSummary': "The 'Simply Bali With Water Sport Activities' package is a 5-day tour that takes you to the beautiful island of Bali. You'll spend your days exploring the stunning beaches, lush green landscapes, and vibrant culture of this Indonesian paradise. Your itinerary will include visits to famous water sports spots like Kuta Beach, Nusa Dua, and Seminyak, where you can try your hand at surfing, snorkeling, or simply relaxing in the sun. You'll also have the opportunity to take a scenic boat tour around the island's picturesque coastline, visit ancient temples like Tanah Lot and Uluwatu, and experience the local cuisine and nightlife. With its perfect blend of adventure, relaxation, and cultural immersion, this package is ideal for travelers looking to unwind in a tropical paradise.", 'thumbnailImage': 'BaliWaterSport267.jpg', 'images': ['balicouple.jpg', 'BannanaBoat.jpg', 'BaliAdventure.jpg', 'NusaPenida753.jpg', 'Bali75390.jpg'], 'visitingCountries': ['Indonesia'], 'departureCities': ['Hyderabad', 'Dehra Dun', 'Vadodara', 'Kozhikode', 'Kannur', 'Madurai', 'Mumbai', 'Indore', 'Nagpur', 'Goa', 'Varanasi', 'Kanpur', 'Chennai', 'Chandigarh', 'Kolkata', 'Guwahati', 'Mangalore', 'Lucknow', 'Coimbatore', 'Visakhapatnam', 'Kochi', 'Ahmedabad', 'Thiruvananthapuram', 'Surat', 'Jaipur', 'Raipur', 'Bhopal', 'Aurangabad', 'Delhi', 'Bangalore', 'Jammu', 'Pune', 'Bhubaneswar', 'Patna'], 'packageItinerary': {'summary': "The 'Simply Bali With Water Sport Activities' package is a 5-day tour that takes you to the beautiful island of Bali. You'll spend your days exploring the stunning beaches, lush green landscapes, and vibrant culture of this Indonesian paradise. Your itinerary will include visits to famous water sports spots like Kuta Beach, Nusa Dua, and Seminyak, where you can try your hand at surfing, snorkeling, or simply relaxing in the sun. You'll also have the opportunity to take a scenic boat tour around the island's picturesque coastline, visit ancient temples like Tanah Lot and Uluwatu, and experience the local cuisine and nightlife. With its perfect blend of adventure, relaxation, and cultural immersion, this package is ideal for travelers looking to unwind in a tropical paradise.", 'itinerary': ['Arrive at Bali (PVT basis) Welcome to Bali – Arrival at the Ngurah Rai, Bali International Airport, meet & greet by our local guide who led you to the parking area to board on vehicle for your transfer to your hotel. It takes about 20 minutes’ drive from airport to your hotel or more depending on the traffic. Upon arrival at the hotel, directly check in and freshen up.', 'Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. An ideal Bali holiday is incomplete without water sports & what better than the famous Tanjung Benoa beach. This beach best known for its aquatic adventure is located in the Benoa peninsula far away from the hustle & bustle. North of Nusa Dua this beach offers a wide range of water sports from Parasailing to Banana boat ride & so on. Please check with our representatives for all the water sports information. Many shacks & restaurants lined up along the beach make sure that your tummy is full & you enjoy the most. Includes: - 1 x Jet Ski, Banana Boat. Complimentary 1 x Parasailing or Flying Fish', 'Full Day ATV Ride & Ayung River Rafting with Lunch (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Experience the Ultimate Adventure with Single ATV or Tandem ATV Bali. Discover the thrills of off-road exploration through Bali’s scenic landscape. Unleash your Inner explorer and create lasting memories with single and tandem ride experience in Bali Inclusion: - Clean Towels, Safety Briefing, Boots, Helmet, Personal Insurance (6 – 65 years), Professional ATV Guide, Locker Enjoy Local Lunch. Later proceed to Ayung River Rafting. Ayung river rafting Bali rapid class can be categories and suitable for beginners. So if you are first Timer and not goo swimmer, Ayung River Rafting adventure is suitable for you. Ayung river has 10 KM route and 2 hours rafting duration. Professional rafting guide is always accompanied with you and give you instructions on thing to do during rafting trip. Inclusion: - Free Coffee & Tea, Snack, Safety equipment, Insurance Coverage, Full use of Lockers, Changing Room, Shower including towel & Soap Return to hotel post the tour and spend the overnight in Bali.', 'West Nusa Penida Island Tour with Lunch (SIC Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today proceed to enjoy West Nusa Penida Island Tour. Highlights: - Kelingking Beach, Angel Billabong, Broken Beach, Snorkeling Oceanic Pool', 'Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. Extension Nights: Travel Validity: 01 Oct – 19 Dec 2024 & 07 Jan – 31 Mar 2025 CATEGORY HOTELS PAKAGE COST: PER PERSON IN USD SINGLE TWIN / DOUBLE TRIPLE CHILD WITH BED CHILD NO BED STANDARD Hotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in Bali USD 40 USD 32 USD 32 USD 25 USD 10 VALUE Antanya Hotel Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali USD 50 USD 50 USD 50 USD 25 USD 10 PREMIUM Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar in Bali USD 95 USD 90 USD 90 USD 40 USD 15 Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Standard Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or Similar in Dubai USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Value Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Premium Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Black Out Dates Surcharge - 20-Dec-2024 to 6-Jan-2025 New Year and Christmas // 26 Jan – 02 Feb 2025 Chinese New year // 28 Mar – 03 Apr 2025 Nyepi Day']}, 'hashKey': '4023db84ae35f21ab9948252a4514b24956c16014cccbaeefa7b3f154eee8f68', 'pkgSubtypeId': 4, 'pkgSubtypeName': 'FIT', 'pkgTypeId': 1}}]}}
2025-02-03 20:55:49,918 - INFO - Package found in ES: {'packageId': 'PKG012812', 'packageName': 'Simply Bali With Water Sport Activities', 'packageTheme': ['Family', 'Adventure', 'Couple Special'], 'days': 5, 'cities': [{'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}], 'highlights': [], 'pdfName': 'PKG012812_0_20250108174641.pdf', 'price': 70052.0, 'minimumPrice': 70052.0, 'packageData': "Package ID: PKG012812 is named 'Simply Bali With Water Sport Activities' and spans 5 days. The itinerary includes:\nDay 1 - Bali, Meals: N/A, Description: Arrive at Bali (PVT basis) Welcome to Bali – Arrival at the Ngurah Rai, Bali International Airport, meet & greet by our local guide who led you to the parking area to board on vehicle for your transfer to your hotel. It takes about 20 minutes’ drive from airport to your hotel or more depending on the traffic. Upon arrival at the hotel, directly check in and freshen up., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 2 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. An ideal Bali holiday is incomplete without water sports & what better than the famous Tanjung Benoa beach. This beach best known for its aquatic adventure is located in the Benoa peninsula far away from the hustle & bustle. North of Nusa Dua this beach offers a wide range of water sports from Parasailing to Banana boat ride & so on. Please check with our representatives for all the water sports information. Many shacks & restaurants lined up along the beach make sure that your tummy is full & you enjoy the most. Includes: - 1 x Jet Ski, Banana Boat. Complimentary 1 x Parasailing or Flying Fish, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 3 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast and Local Lunch, Description: Full Day ATV Ride & Ayung River Rafting with Lunch (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Experience the Ultimate Adventure with Single ATV or Tandem ATV Bali. Discover the thrills of off-road exploration through Bali’s scenic landscape. Unleash your Inner explorer and create lasting memories with single and tandem ride experience in Bali Inclusion: - Clean Towels, Safety Briefing, Boots, Helmet, Personal Insurance (6 – 65 years), Professional ATV Guide, Locker Enjoy Local Lunch. Later proceed to Ayung River Rafting. Ayung river rafting Bali rapid class can be categories and suitable for beginners. So if you are first Timer and not goo swimmer, Ayung River Rafting adventure is suitable for you. Ayung river has 10 KM route and 2 hours rafting duration. Professional rafting guide is always accompanied with you and give you instructions on thing to do during rafting trip. Inclusion: - Free Coffee & Tea, Snack, Safety equipment, Insurance Coverage, Full use of Lockers, Changing Room, Shower including towel & Soap Return to hotel post the tour and spend the overnight in Bali., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 4 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast and Local Lunch, Description: West Nusa Penida Island Tour with Lunch (SIC Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today proceed to enjoy West Nusa Penida Island Tour. Highlights: - Kelingking Beach, Angel Billabong, Broken Beach, Snorkeling Oceanic Pool, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 5 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. Extension Nights: Travel Validity: 01 Oct – 19 Dec 2024 & 07 Jan – 31 Mar 2025 CATEGORY HOTELS PAKAGE COST: PER PERSON IN USD SINGLE TWIN / DOUBLE TRIPLE CHILD WITH BED CHILD NO BED STANDARD Hotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in Bali USD 40 USD 32 USD 32 USD 25 USD 10 VALUE Antanya Hotel Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali USD 50 USD 50 USD 50 USD 25 USD 10 PREMIUM Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar in Bali USD 95 USD 90 USD 90 USD 40 USD 15 Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Standard Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or Similar in Dubai USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Value Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Premium Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Black Out Dates Surcharge - 20-Dec-2024 to 6-Jan-2025 New Year and Christmas // 26 Jan – 02 Feb 2025 Chinese New year // 28 Mar – 03 Apr 2025 Nyepi Day, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nThe price is 70052.0. Hotels envisaged include: \nHotel\xa0Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali\n, \nHotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in\xa0Bali\n, \nHotel\xa0Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or\xa0Similar in Bali\n. Meals include: Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included. Inclusions: 04 nights stay at the selected hotel option or similar in Kuta. Daily breakfast, except on Day 1 Airport / hotel / airport transfers on (PVT Basis) Meet & Greet assistance at the airport English Speaking Driver during Transfer & Tour Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (PVT Basis) Full Day: ATV Ride & Ayung River Rafting with Local Lunch (PVT Basis) West Nusa Penida Island Tour with Local Lunch (SIC Basis) Complimentary Welcome drink upon arrival at the Hotel & Villa Complimentary Balinese Sarong per person (adult only) as welcome gift on arrival (Adult only) Complimentary 01 bottle of Mineral Water per person on arrival Free Wi-Fi at Hotel/Villa/ Resort area Travel Insurance (Valid for the age group till 60 Yrs.). Exclusions: TCS & GST Indonesia Visa Charges