2025-02-03 20:55:49,942 - INFO - Elasticsearch response: {'took': 2, 'timed_out': False, '_shards': {'total': 1, 'successful': 1, 'skipped': 0, 'failed': 0}, 'hits': {'total': {'value': 1, 'relation': 'eq'}, 'max_score': 6.6995, 'hits': [{'_index': 'tcildatav1', '_id': 'PKG012817', '_score': 6.6995, '_source': {'packageId': 'PKG012817', 'packageName': 'Simply Bali Split Stay - 4N Hotel and 2N Villa', 'packageTheme': ['Couple Special', 'Family', 'Adventure'], 'days': 7, 'cities': [{'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}, {'cityName': 'Bali', 'geoLocation': {'lat': 0.0, 'lon': 0.0}}], 'highlights': [], 'pdfName': 'PKG012817_0_20250108184924.pdf', 'price': 71843.0, 'minimumPrice': 71843.0, 'packageData': "Package ID: PKG012817 is named 'Simply Bali Split Stay - 4N Hotel and 2N Villa' and spans 7 days. The itinerary includes:\nDay 1 - Bali, Meals: N/A, Description: Arrive at Bali (PVT basis) Welcome to Bali – Arrival at the Ngurah Rai, Bali International Airport, meet & greet by our local guide who led you to the parking area to board on vehicle for your transfer to your hotel. It takes about 20 minutes’ drive from airport to your hotel or more depending on the traffic. Upon arrival at the hotel, directly check in and freshen up., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 2 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Full Day Kintamani Hot Spring & Ubud village Tour –With Tanah Lot Sunset Tour (PVT Basis) Pick up for Celuk Silver Art Village Celuk Village is a traditional village which famous for the incredible gold and silver handicrafts are available around this area for very low prices. As you enter the neighborhood, you're going to feel as if you were in a jewelry exhibition. On either side of the road are established many art shops showcasing their finest works inside a glass display case. We will visit one of the best gold and silver art works in celuk village. You can take a closer look at them to appreciate it and buy some if you really like it or you can made custom jewelry based on your design. Visit Mas Wooden Carved Art Village Mas Village is one of traditional villages in Bali fundamentally as an artistic countryside by focusing the art of wood carving. This village is famous in the island as Bali Wood Carving Center located in Ubud sub district and Gianyar Regency. It owns the typical style of wood carving art by placing forward the distinguish synergy of the humanism and naturalism Visit Kintamani Hot Spring Kintamani Hot Spring features eight natural hot spring pools and one warm olympic sized pool. Heated deep within the earth, minerals from the colorless and odorless hot spring brings healing and curative powers. Enjoy a relaxing dip with the majestic panorama! *Inclusions: Natural Hot Spring Pools, Toya Water Slide with Tubes, Towel & Locker, Change & Shower Room, Facility Continue to visit Tanah Lot for Sunset Tour Tanah Lot Temple is one of the most popular Bali Places of Interest and its an ancient Hindu shrine perched on top of an outcrop amidst constantly crashing waves the temple is simply among Bali not to be missed icons. The onshore site is dotted with smaller shrines alongside visitor’s leisure facilities that comprise restaurants, shops and cultural park presenting regular dance performances. The temple is located in the Beraban village of the Tabanan regency, an approximate 20 Km northwest of Kuta and is included on most of the Bali western and central regions., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 3 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Salty Air! Sandy Hair! Feel the tropical breeze and get closer to Indian Ocean with our selected Water Sports Activity. Pick up for Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (Incl. 1 x Jet Ski – Banana Boat Ride) and Complimentary 1 x Parasailing or Flying Fish, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 4 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Day at Leisure Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today Day is at leisure to explore Bali or shopping at the local market., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 5 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Kuta – Villa (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Pick up for Inter Hotel Transfers to Villa, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 6 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Day at Leisure Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today Day is at leisure to explore Bali or shopping at the local market., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 7 - Bali, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Standard Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or Similar in Dubai USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Value Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Premium Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Value Grand Kesambi Villa USD 65 USD 15 USD 15 USD 15 USD 15 Black Out Dates Surcharge - 20-Dec-2024 to 6-Jan-2025 New Year and Christmas // 26 Jan – 02 Feb 2025 Chinese New year // 28 Mar – 03 Apr 2025 Nyepi Day, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nThe price is 71843.0. Hotels envisaged include: \n4 Nights Hotel\xa0Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or\xa0Similar in Bali\n2 Nights\xa0Grand Kesambi Resort & Villa – One Bedroom Pool Villa\n, \n4 Nights Hotel Siesta Legian ( Superior Room) or similar in\xa0Bali\n2 Nights\xa0Grand Kesambi Resort & Villa – One Bedroom Pool Villa\n, \n4 Nights Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar in Bali\n2 Nights\xa0Grand Kesambi Resort & Villa – One Bedroom Pool Villa\n. Meals include: Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included. Inclusions: Experience 04 night’s hotel stay + 02 nights villa stay Daily breakfast, except on Day 1 Airport / hotel / airport transfers on (PVT Basis) Meet & Greet assistance at the airport English Speaking Driver during Transfer & Tour Half Day Water Sports with Uluwatu Temple Tour Followed by Kecak Dance (PVT Basis) Full Day Kintamani Hot Spring & Ubud village Tour –With Tanah Lot Sunset Tour (PVT Basis) Complimentary Welcome drink upon arrival at the Hotel & Villa Complimentary Balinese Sarong per person (adult only) as welcome gift on arrival (Adult only) Complimentary 01 bottle of Mineral Water per person on arrival Free Wi-Fi at Hotel/Villa/ Resort area Travel Insurance (Valid for the age group till 60 Yrs.). Exclusions: TCS & GST Indonesia Visa Charges Departure PCR test, if applicable All flights service Meals not mentioned in the itinerary. Any tips for guide & Driver Anything not mentioned in the inclusions. Pre & Post tour services & cost Expenditure of a personal nature (Such as uses of Mini – Bar & Refrigerator, laundry service, telephone call, camera fee, tips & Etc) All drink and beverages Hotel promotional rates not valid during Black out Period / Surcharge Dates / Stop Sales on Hotel Tourism Tax (if applicable) Midnight surcharge Blackout Dates: 15 DEC 2024 - 06 JAN 2025 The rates are valid for minimum 02 adults travelling together at all times.. Product Terms and Conditions: Terms and Conditions: The upgrade hotel prices are subject to availability at the time of booking. The upgrade hotel prices DO NOT GUARANTEE rooms at the envisaged hotels. The upgrade hotel rooms are subject to availability at the time of booking. For the upgrade hotel, In case the hotel chosen is unavailable we will provide with multiple options of similar category hotel. The rates are valid for minimum 02 adults travelling together at all times. During Peak Season: Minimum 2 Nights Stay is required No Check Out period on 31 December 2024 and 01 January 2025 Nyepi Day (Silent Day) is on 29 March 2025. No outdoor activity is allowed, and Airport will be closed from 05.59 am 29 March 2025 to 06.00 am 30 March 2025 Compulsory New Year Dinner will be Applicable according to the Resort The rates are not valid on block out dates. Surcharges as and when applicable will be advised and passengers would be requested to pay the same Surcharges could be over and above the total package price quoted to the passengers at the time of booking. Guests are requested to check with sales staff before booking their on-wards/connecting flights. The rates are subject to availability of hotel accommodation and sightseeing tours at the time of booking. We reserve the right to use an alternate hotel accommodation of an equal or higher standard. If we source a more expensive alternative, we reserve the right to re-quote based on the higher rates. Prices are not valid during Trade Fair periods. Rates are valid for Indian Passport holders only. International Check in time is 1400 hours / Check out time is 1100 hours, early check in and checkout is subject to availability and cannot be guaranteed. Transfers wherever included are without night surcharges. No refunds either in part or in full will be made for any unutilized service. All the sightseeing tours and excursions are organized by local companies. The timings and days of operation are subject to alteration. Changes if any will be intimated at the time of booking. Sightseeing’s tours are strictly based on whether conditions and also local service providers have rights to cancel the sightseeing tours without prior notice. Rates subject to change without prior notice and also for clients traveling during weekends. Offer if any can be withdrawn at any point without prior notice. Bookings once confirmed are subject to cancellation charges which shall be advised at that time. TC is not responsible for any change in the price due to factors not in the control of the organization. As a practice all international hotels charge a security deposit via credit card or cash, at the time of check- in for each room. The amount will vary according to the hotel and is refunded back to the clients upon check-out. Debit cards should not be offered as it will be charged immediately and refunded only after 2-3 weeks. If any additional services or mini bar or any other service is utilized at the hotel, the hotel reserves the right to charge the same on this security deposit provided by the client. TC would not be responsible for these transactions and these are solely between the hotels and the clients.. Highlights of the package: .", 'packageSummary': "The 'Simply Bali Split Stay - 4N Hotel and 2N Villa' package is a 7-day tour that takes you to the beautiful island of Bali. You'll spend four nights in a hotel and two nights in a villa, immersing yourself in the local culture and natural beauty of this Indonesian paradise. Your journey will take you through various parts of Bali, where you can explore stunning beaches, lush green landscapes, and vibrant temples. The itinerary includes visits to famous landmarks such as Uluwatu Temple, Tirta Empul Temple, and Tanah Lot Temple, as well as opportunities to enjoy water sports, yoga classes, and traditional Balinese dance performances. You'll also have time to relax in your hotel or villa, take a leisurely stroll through the local markets, and indulge in delicious Indonesian cuisine.", 'thumbnailImage': 'bali5.jpg', 'images': ['balicouple.jpg', 'Tanah_Lot_Temple_New_Bali_&53.jpg', 'BALI_BananaBoat.jpg', 'Bali_753.jpg', 'Bali1.jpg', 'Batur.jpg', 'Bali9.jpg'], 'visitingCountries': ['Indonesia'], 'departureCities': ['Raipur', 'Mangalore', 'Mumbai', 'Kochi', 'Nagpur', 'Surat', 'Dehra Dun', 'Kolkata', 'Kannur', 'Kanpur', 'Jammu', 'Pune', 'Varanasi', 'Jaipur', 'Indore', 'Delhi', 'Vadodara', 'Thiruvananthapuram', 'Guwahati', 'Chandigarh', 'Bhopal', 'Visakhapatnam', 'Goa', 'Coimbatore', 'Hyderabad', 'Bangalore', 'Ahmedabad', 'Chennai', 'Lucknow', 'Aurangabad', 'Kozhikode', 'Madurai', 'Bhubaneswar', 'Patna'], 'packageItinerary': {'summary': "The 'Simply Bali Split Stay - 4N Hotel and 2N Villa' package is a 7-day tour that takes you to the beautiful island of Bali. You'll spend four nights in a hotel and two nights in a villa, immersing yourself in the local culture and natural beauty of this Indonesian paradise. Your journey will take you through various parts of Bali, where you can explore stunning beaches, lush green landscapes, and vibrant temples. The itinerary includes visits to famous landmarks such as Uluwatu Temple, Tirta Empul Temple, and Tanah Lot Temple, as well as opportunities to enjoy water sports, yoga classes, and traditional Balinese dance performances. You'll also have time to relax in your hotel or villa, take a leisurely stroll through the local markets, and indulge in delicious Indonesian cuisine.", 'itinerary': ['Arrive at Bali (PVT basis) Welcome to Bali – Arrival at the Ngurah Rai, Bali International Airport, meet & greet by our local guide who led you to the parking area to board on vehicle for your transfer to your hotel. It takes about 20 minutes’ drive from airport to your hotel or more depending on the traffic. Upon arrival at the hotel, directly check in and freshen up.', "Full Day Kintamani Hot Spring & Ubud village Tour –With Tanah Lot Sunset Tour (PVT Basis) Pick up for Celuk Silver Art Village Celuk Village is a traditional village which famous for the incredible gold and silver handicrafts are available around this area for very low prices. As you enter the neighborhood, you're going to feel as if you were in a jewelry exhibition. On either side of the road are established many art shops showcasing their finest works inside a glass display case. We will visit one of the best gold and silver art works in celuk village. You can take a closer look at them to appreciate it and buy some if you really like it or you can made custom jewelry based on your design. Visit Mas Wooden Carved Art Village Mas Village is one of traditional villages in Bali fundamentally as an artistic countryside by focusing the art of wood carving. This village is famous in the island as Bali Wood Carving Center located in Ubud sub district and Gianyar Regency. It owns the typical style of wood carving art by placing forward the distinguish synergy of the humanism and naturalism Visit Kintamani Hot Spring Kintamani Hot Spring features eight natural hot spring pools and one warm olympic sized pool. Heated deep within the earth, minerals from the colorless and odorless hot spring brings healing and curative powers. Enjoy a relaxing dip with the majestic panorama! *Inclusions: Natural Hot Spring Pools, Toya Water Slide with Tubes, Towel & Locker, Change & Shower Room, Facility Continue to visit Tanah Lot for Sunset Tour Tanah Lot Temple is one of the most popular Bali Places of Interest and its an ancient Hindu shrine perched on top of an outcrop amidst constantly crashing waves the temple is simply among Bali not to be missed icons. The onshore site is dotted with smaller shrines alongside visitor’s leisure facilities that comprise restaurants, shops and cultural park presenting regular dance performances. The temple is located in the Beraban village of the Tabanan regency, an approximate 20 Km northwest of Kuta and is included on most of the Bali western and central regions.", 'Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Salty Air! Sandy Hair! Feel the tropical breeze and get closer to Indian Ocean with our selected Water Sports Activity. Pick up for Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (Incl. 1 x Jet Ski – Banana Boat Ride) and Complimentary 1 x Parasailing or Flying Fish', 'Day at Leisure Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today Day is at leisure to explore Bali or shopping at the local market.', 'Kuta – Villa (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Pick up for Inter Hotel Transfers to Villa', 'Day at Leisure Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today Day is at leisure to explore Bali or shopping at the local market.', 'Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Standard Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or Similar in Dubai USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Value Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Premium Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Value Grand Kesambi Villa USD 65 USD 15 USD 15 USD 15 USD 15 Black Out Dates Surcharge - 20-Dec-2024 to 6-Jan-2025 New Year and Christmas // 26 Jan – 02 Feb 2025 Chinese New year // 28 Mar – 03 Apr 2025 Nyepi Day']}, 'hashKey': '5d925d9e292a3224b83d076dc1e98977d453fec96eed0e6cfa0bd4ee42639a97', 'pkgSubtypeId': 4, 'pkgSubtypeName': 'FIT', 'pkgTypeId': 1}}]}}
