d silver art works in celuk village. You can take a closer look at them to appreciate it and buy some if you really like it or you can made custom jewelry based on your design. Visit Mas Wooden Carved Art Village Mas Village is one of traditional villages in Bali fundamentally as an artistic countryside by focusing the art of wood carving. This village is famous in the island as Bali Wood Carving Center located in Ubud sub district and Gianyar Regency. It owns the typical style of wood carving art by placing forward the distinguish synergy of the humanism and naturalism Visit Kintamani Hot Spring Kintamani Hot Spring features eight natural hot spring pools and one warm olympic sized pool. Heated deep within the earth, minerals from the colorless and odorless hot spring brings healing and curative powers. Enjoy a relaxing dip with the majestic panorama! *Inclusions: Natural Hot Spring Pools, Toya Water Slide with Tubes, Towel & Locker, Change & Shower Room, Facility Continue to visit Tanah Lot for Sunset Tour Tanah Lot Temple is one of the most popular Bali Places of Interest and its an ancient Hindu shrine perched on top of an outcrop amidst constantly crashing waves the temple is simply among Bali not to be missed icons. The onshore site is dotted with smaller shrines alongside visitor’s leisure facilities that comprise restaurants, shops and cultural park presenting regular dance performances. The temple is located in the Beraban village of the Tabanan regency, an approximate 20 Km northwest of Kuta and is included on most of the Bali western and central regions.", 'Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Salty Air! Sandy Hair! Feel the tropical breeze and get closer to Indian Ocean with our selected Water Sports Activity. Pick up for Water Sports at Tanjung Benoa Beach (Incl. 1 x Jet Ski – Banana Boat Ride) and Complimentary 1 x Parasailing or Flying Fish', 'Day at Leisure Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today Day is at leisure to explore Bali or shopping at the local market.', 'Kuta – Villa (PVT Basis) Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Pick up for Inter Hotel Transfers to Villa', 'Day at Leisure Enjoy Breakfast in Hotel. Today Day is at leisure to explore Bali or shopping at the local market.', 'Depart from Kuta Morning after breakfast; you will be transferred to the airport for your flight back home to India. * The itinerary is tentative and subject to change without prior notice. Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Standard Hotel Siesta Legian (Superior Room) or Similar in Dubai USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Value Hotel Antanya Kuta (Deluxe Room) / Solia Legian Bali (Solia Deluxe) Or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Premium Kuta Paradiso (Deluxe Room) or Similar USD 50 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 USD 17 Surcharge Dates Travel Validity: 20 DEC 2024 – 05 JAN 2025 Category Hotels Pakage Cost: Per Person Per Day In USD Single Twin/Double Triple ChildWith Bed ChildNo Bed Value Grand Kesambi Villa USD 65 USD 15 USD 15 USD 15 USD 15 Black Out Dates Surcharge - 20-Dec-2024 to 6-Jan-2025 New Year and Christmas // 26 Jan – 02 Feb 2025 Chinese New year // 28 Mar – 03 Apr 2025 Nyepi Day']), pkgSubtypeId=4, pkgSubtypeName='FIT', pkgTypeId=1) score=6.6995
