d to the southern tip of Bali for Uluwatu Sunset tour. Uluwatu Temple, or Pura Luhur Uluwatu, is renowned for its magnificent location, perched on top of a steep cliff approximately 70 meters above the waves. As one of the 6 key temples considered to be Bali's spiritual pillars, Uluwatu also offers a splendid sunset backdrop. It is definitely one of the top places in Bali for witnessing a delightful sunset, with direct views overlooking the beautiful waves of the Indian Ocean., GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nDay 5 - Seminyak, Meals: Breakfast, Description: Departure Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel Pick up from the hotel to transfer to the Airport according to the scheduled Flight. * The itinerary is tentative and subjected to change without prior notice. Extension Night Travel Validity: 16 September – 20 December 2024 CATEGORY HOTELS PACKAGE COST: PER PERSON IN USD SINGLE TWIN / DOUBLE TRIPLE CHILD WITH BED CHILD NO BED Deluxe The Lokha Ubud Resort Villas and Spa 97 55 55 44 8 Villa Kayu Raja Seminyak 101 58 58 46 10 Premium Maya Ubud Resort & Spa 206 118 118 95 27 Villa Jerami and Spa 135 77 77 62 15 EXTENSION NIGHT Travel Validity: 06 JAN – 23 MARCH 2025 CATEGORY HOTELS PACKAGE COST: PER PERSON IN USD SINGLE TWIN / DOUBLE TRIPLE CHILD WITH BED CHILD NO BED Deluxe The Lokha Ubud Resort Villas and Spa 121 69 69 55 10 Villa Kayu Raja Seminyak 126 73 73 58 13 Premium Maya Ubud Resort & Spa 258 148 148 119 34 Villa Jerami and Spa 169 96 96 78 19, GeoLocation: (Lat: 0.0, Lon: 0.0).\nThe price is 36545.0. Hotels envisaged include: Overnight stay at the Hotels, Overnight stay at the Hotels, Overnight stay at the Hotels. Meals include: Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included, Breakfast Included. Inclusions: 02 nights stay at the selected hotel option or similar Ubud 02 nights stay at the selected hotel option or similar Seminyak Meet & Greet assistance at the Airport Return Airport & Inter Hotel Transfer on Private basis Half Day Benoa Beach Tour including Banana Boat on 