 itinerary=['Kuta Arrival at the Ngurah Rai, Bali International Airport, meet & greet by our local guide who led you to the parking area to board on vehicle for your transfer to your hotel. It takes about 20 minutes’ drive from airport to your hotel or more depending on the traffic. Upon arrival at the hotel, directly check in and freshen up.', 'Half Day ATV Quad Bike on Private Basis & Half Day Benoa Beach Tour including Banana Boat on private basis Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel For a hard core adventurer or a novice, off-roading is the most appealing word & what better than Quad Biking while in Bali. Ride off the beaten track during your Bali vacation on your own All-Terrain Vehicle (ATV). Follow an experienced guide along a challenging track, suitable for all skill levels. One can also enjoy as a co-pilot if you do not want to do it independently. No driving license required & safety is of utmost priority here. Glide past a picturesque landscape of rice fields, bamboo forest, and lush riverside flanked by traditional Balinese villages. It is an ultimate thrill for a couple of hours, you will just want to keep it going. An ideal Bali holiday is incomplete without water sports & what better than the famous Tanjung Benoa beach. This beach best known for its aquatic adventure is located in the Benoa peninsula far away from the hustle & bustle. North of Nusa Dua this beach offers a wide range of water sports from Parasailing to Banana boat ride & so on. Please check with our representatives for all the water sports information. Many shacks & restaurants lined up along the beach make sure that your tummy is full & you enjoy the most.', 'Half Day Authentic Balinese Massage (60 min) on Private Basis + Bali Swing on Private Basis Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel A Bali holiday isn’t complete without an authentic spa experience. Balinese spa treatments are well-known the world over for their healing properties as well as the hospitality by the locals. Refresh your mind, body & soul with a perfect blend of traditional therapeutic remedies & modern day spa rituals. Enjoy this delightful massage & rejuvenate yourself to the core. Swings in Bali are the most trending activities across all social media platforms. And the experiences definitely justify the popularity. Set in Ubud you must try and enjoy this incredible experience. A professional swing guide, will company you to catch the unforgettable memory. Proper set of instructions will guide you through the equipment & safety standards. Soak in the pleasure of being a free bird, reminiscing through your childhood days.', 'Transfer from Kuta to Ubud, Sunset Dinner Cruise on Private Basis Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel Inter Hotel Transfer Kuta Hotel to Ubud Hotel on Private Basis No better way than a Sunset Dinner Cruise on a balmy tropical evening. As the daylight fades & the Sun goes into oblivion, you set off on a relaxing short voyage around the alluring Bali harbor & its surrounding areas. Seize the moments, in the cool & calm environs of the top deck aboard the vessel. A plethora of activities will make your evening more memorable. Soak in to the live musical experiences at the bridge deck, savour wide array of delectable international buffet dinner & also witnesses the live Cabaret show. Dance the night away like no one’s watching. Definitely a treat for all age groups but highly recommended for the honeymooners. A remarkable evening well spent on board the Sunset dinner cruise will always give you nostalgia for life.', 'Full Day Lempuyang Temple Tour on Private Basis Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel Ever wondered what its like actually to visit The Gates of Heaven. If you are visiting Bali, then this popular place must be on your list of things to see and do. Most people visit here to get an epic shot between the Candi Bentar â€“ The Gateway. This Candi Bentar is a split gateway seen in almost all Balinese entrances of religious compounds. Usually, these gateways have staircases that lead to its centre point. The two sides represent the Balinese concept of duality and the importance of maintaining a balance between darkness & the bright forces. While you will see Candi Bentars everywhere in Bali, the Gates of Heaven at Lempuyang Temple is by far the most visited. Instagram has turned this place into a magnet for everyone visiting Bali.', 'Transfer from Ubud to Seminyak Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel Inter Hotel Transfer Ubud Hotel to Seminyak Hotel on Private Basis.', 'Full Day Nusa Penida West Island Tour with Local Lunch on SIC Basis Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel A Full day tour to Nusa Penida West Island Tour will give you an experience you will never forget. This is a relatively undeveloped island southeast of the mainland of Bali. Nusa means Island and Penida means priests in Balinese. You won’t find the snazzy beach clubs, organic cafes or trendy restaurants here, but Nusa Penida is still worthy of a visit. It houses some of the most photogenic sights in Bali. In Nusa Penida West Island Tour, we visit 04 Points - Klingking bay, Angel billabong, Broken beach and Crystal Bay.', 'Departure: Enjoy Breakfast at the Hotel Pick up from the hotel to transfer to the Airport according to the scheduled Flight. * The itinerary is tentative and subjected to change without prior notice.']), pkgSubtypeId=4, pkgSubtypeName='FIT', pkgTypeId=1) score=6.6995
