o the hotel and is refunded back to the clients upon check-out. Debit cards should not be offered as it will be charged immediately and refunded only after 2-3 weeks. If any additional services or mini bar or any other service is utilized at the hotel, the hotel reserves the right to charge the same on this security deposit provided by the client. TCIL would not be responsible for these transactions and these are solely between the hotels and the clients.. Highlights of the package: .", 'packageSummary': "The 'Memorable Bali - Honeymoon Special' package is a 5-day romantic getaway to the beautiful island of Bali. This tour takes you through the vibrant city of Kuta, where you'll experience the best of Balinese culture and luxury. Your journey will be filled with exciting activities such as snorkeling in crystal-clear waters, exploring the famous Uluwatu Temple perched on a cliff overlooking the Indian Ocean, and watching the mesmerizing sunset at Seminyak Beach. You'll also have the opportunity to indulge in rejuvenating spa treatments, enjoy a romantic candlelit dinner at a beachfront restaurant, and take a leisurely stroll through the lush green landscapes of Tegalalang rice fields.", 'thumbnailImage': 'Nusa_Penida_753.jpg', 'images': ['Bali1.jpg', 'Bananaboat.jpg', 'Baliswing_new_753.jpeg', 'NusaPenida.png', '47777_Ubud_Green_Rice_Bali753.jpg'], 'visitingCountries': ['Indonesia'], 'departureCities': ['Goa', 'Bhopal', 'Mumbai', 'Pune', 'Chennai', 'Nagpur', 'Allahabad', 'Bagdogra', 'Kochi', 'Udaipur', 'Guwahati', 'Delhi', 'Mangalore', 'Thiruvananthapuram', 'Kozhikode', 'Jammu', 'Indore', 'Ahmedabad', 'Kolkata', 'Chandigarh', 'Patna', 'Varanasi', 'Jaipur', 'Lucknow', 'Surat', 'Aurangabad', 'Bhubaneswar', 'Amritsar', 'Srinagar', 'Bangalore', 'Hyderabad', 'Imphal'], 'packageItinerary': {'summary': "The 'Memorable Bali - Honeymoon Special' package is a 5-day romantic getaway to the beautiful island of Bali. This tour takes you through the vibrant city of Kuta, where yo